{"tid":2507590,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[國泰告急] 國泰再推自願離職計畫 放無薪假","createTime":"2021-04-28T05:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T07:15:13.000Z","uid":362414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee06fe7b3a9fac84d324ae831d431e2883a47be","tid":2507590,"uid":362414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:56:56.000Z","msg":"早前市傳國泰（0293）可能會在6月再度裁員，及另推員工帶薪假計劃。由於新冠疫情仍持續影響該公司的營運，故此將再推出自願離職計劃。<br />\n<br />\n信中指，航運復甦步伐及國際旅行需求仍然非常不確定，預計將在相當長的時間內，集團需繼續維持基本航班，會繼續採取措施來去管理職位及保持快捷的反應。信中又指，公司不希望見到更多有價值的同事離開，但認為，為部分出於個人原因，或尋求其他機會的員工，提供選擇是值得的。可以參與自願離職計劃的員工包括空中服務人員、機師及前線人員。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7333/5406721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7333%2F5406721&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0oMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=ea90abbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7333/5406721</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/618013/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA-%E6%96%99%E7%9F%AD%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%9F%E7%84%A1%E6%98%8E%E9%A1%AF%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84-%E5%90%91%E8%8B%A5%E5%B9%B2%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%B5%84%E5%88%A5%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E8%87%AA%E9%A1%98%E9%9B%A2%E8%81%B7%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F618013%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E6%2596%2599%25E7%259F%25AD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%259C%259F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2598%258E%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2596%2584-%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%2588%25A5%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%2587%25AA%25E9%25A1%2598%25E9%259B%25A2%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0oMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=62ff5872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/618013/%E5%9C%